== NOTE FROM NEIL ==
Since this article contains references to acts of illegality, I must stress 
that the opinions expressed here are not necessarily those of World Of 
Amiga. 

Additionally, console game prices are so high because of the massive fees 
companies have to pay for the privelage of writing a game on the console, 
often in excess of a 45,000 pound lump sum before development has even 
begun!

